bio.openEndedText: Family time is the best time, I enjoy scuba diving, riding my bike, flying planes and of course spending time with my family.

Thank you for considering one of my cars. Read the reviews and I think you will see for yourself that you are selecting a car from someone that not only cares about their cars, but the people in them. 

All my vehicles are well maintained with low mileage and EVERY CAR AVAILABLE is still under the MANUFACTURES WARRANTY. I can’t stress how important that is.  This ensures you’re selecting a safe car. 

I don’t cut corners for the sake of profit.  I put the best tires on my cars, I get all my cars heavily optioned and will not buy a car unless it has lane change warnings, sensors, cameras and if available auto break. 

2 people were saved from a costly accident and possible injuries because the Mercedes E300 braked when they were distracted. 
One of the people, a father could not stop thanking me. He became distracted by his  kids fighting in the back and the auto break prevented an accident. 
That’s why I make sure all my cars have every safety option available. My Jeep is the only one in LA with lane change warnings, back up camera and sensors. Literally has more options then my G65 had. 

Look at my commitment rate and you will see it’s 100 percent.  You never have to worry about being stranded last minute without a car.
I am a true car enthusiast! I love sharing awesome cars with you guys!
